.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-17::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, bellflower, balloon-flower
3 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, rat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, volleyball, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is in an even position##4
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Flower     | bellflower      | daffodil | balloon-flower |
| Pet     | chinchilla | bird      | rat           |
| Sport   | water-polo | climbing  | volleyball    |

