3. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |
| Beverage    | mirinda | tea      | sprite     |
| Pet         | lizard  | goldfish | rat        |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | fishing    | writing |

