.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, collecting, sudoku
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, jazz, blues
3 different pets are kept: cat, fish, lizard
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the fan of jazz##2
2. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of blues is the owner of the fish##1
5. the fan of blues is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
7. the fan of dubstep is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby         | sudoku      | collecting | card-games |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | dubstep      | blues    |
| Pet           | lizard      | cat        | fish       |

 